ast.name: List it Plus
ast.comment:
List It Plus is a helpful checklist script with a slick interface And takes advantage of gestures to give you a completely new experience.
A Very Cool To Do List App, I Will Add More Functions In The Future!

Remember You May Not Edit Or Reproduce In Any Way Or You May Face Criminal Charges! This App Is Only For Personal Enjoyment, That Means No "Copy And Paste" Of Code
Or Modification Of Any Kind, Or Repost Of This App. if You Do Not Accept The Terms Of Use, You Must remove This App From Your Device!
Please Note That All Usage ( Except Your Personal Info Stored In The App ) will Be Recorded!


Full feature list:
✔Slick interface (uses accent color)
✔Smooth animations
✔Use gestures to mark tasks as done, add or delete tasks
✔Easy to use
✔Awesome Live Tile

New in V1.1:
✔Everything is now stored in records
✔Task lists
✔You can now rename your tasks/lists
✔Fixed some bugs
